# Verify energy distribution
energy_dist = np.histogram(data['energy'], bins=20)
print(f'Energy distribution: {energy_dist}')

# Verify spot_size distribution
spot_size_dist = np.histogram(data['spot_size'], bins=50)
print(f'Spot size distribution: {spot_size_dist}')

# Verify intensity distribution
intensity_dist = np.histogram(data['intensity'], bins=20)
print(f'Intensity distribution: {intensity_dist}')

# Verify power distribution
power_dist = np.histogram(data['power'], bins=25)
print(f'Power distribution: {power_dist}')

# Verify cutoff_energy distribution
cutoff_energy_dist = np.histogram(data['cutoff_energy'], bins=20)
print(f'Cutoff energy distribution: {cutoff_energy_dist}')

# Print the complete dataset
print('Complete dataset:')
print(data)
